Batch Integration

# curl commands
```
export FI_BATCH_HOST=127.0.0.1:8088

# (fluentmock-1)
export FI_APIKEY=eyJhY2NvdW50SWQiOiJmbHVlbnRtb2NrIiwicmV0YWlsZXJJZCI6IjEiLCJjcmVhdGVkT24iOiIyMDIzLTAzLTIwVDAwOjAwOjAwIn0=.

curl --location --request POST http://$FI_BATCH_HOST/batch \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--header "apiKey:$FI_APIKEY" \
--data-raw '{
	"queryFile":"virtualPositions.graphql",
	"edgeTypeName": "virtualPositionEdge",
	"outputFile": "file://.?filename=out.csv",
	"outputFormat": "csv",
	"splitCount": 100,
	"variables": {"ref":"%LOC_SYD%", "updatedFrom": "2023-01-01T00:00:00.000", "catalogueRef":"BASE:1"}
}'
```
